## Analysis and Description of the Main Target Image:

**Structure 1 (Left):**
- **Count & Layers:** This structure is composed of 7 blocks and has 5 layers.
- **Spatial Relationships:**
    - **Layer 1 (Bottom):** Two orange cylinders (vertical orientation) placed side-by-side horizontally.
    - **Layer 2:** One yellow rectangular block (horizontal orientation) placed on top of the two orange cylinders, spanning across both.
    - **Layer 3:** Two orange triangular blocks (roof orientation) placed side-by-side on top of the yellow rectangular block, forming a roof-like shape.
    - **Layer 4:** One orange cylinder (vertical orientation) placed centrally on top of the two orange triangular blocks.
    - **Layer 5 (Top):** One orange triangular block (roof orientation) placed on top of the orange cylinder.

**Structure 2 (Right):**
- **Count & Layers:** This structure is composed of 7 blocks and has 7 layers.
- **Spatial Relationships:**
    - **Layer 1 (Bottom):** One green rectangular block (horizontal orientation) serving as the base.
    - **Layer 2:** One orange cylinder (vertical orientation) placed centrally on top of the green rectangular base.
    - **Layer 3:** One yellow rectangular block (horizontal orientation) placed on top of the orange cylinder.
    - **Layer 4:** One green rectangular block (horizontal orientation) placed on top of the yellow rectangular block.
    - **Layer 5:** One orange triangular block (slanted orientation) placed on top of the green rectangular block.
    - **Layer 6:** One blue rectangular block (horizontal orientation) placed on top of the orange triangular block and green rectangular block.
    - **Layer 7 (Top):** One green rectangular block (horizontal orientation) placed on top of the orange triangular block and green rectangular block, completing the top layer.


## Selection of Required Blocks from the Dictionary:

**For Structure 1 (Left):**
- Layer 1: Block index 10 (Orange Cylinder - Vertical) - Quantity: 2
- Layer 2: Block index 6 (Yellow Rectangular - Horizontal) - Quantity: 1
- Layer 3: Block index 14 (Orange Triangular - Roof) - Quantity: 2
- Layer 4: Block index 10 (Orange Cylinder - Vertical) - Quantity: 1
- Layer 5: Block index 14 (Orange Triangular - Roof) - Quantity: 1

**For Structure 2 (Right):**
- Layer 1: Block index 3 (Green Rectangular - Horizontal) - Quantity: 1
- Layer 2: Block index 10 (Orange Cylinder - Vertical) - Quantity: 1
- Layer 3: Block index 6 (Yellow Rectangular - Horizontal) - Quantity: 1
- Layer 4: Block index 3 (Green Rectangular - Horizontal) - Quantity: 1
- Layer 5: Block index 15 (Orange Triangular - Slanted) - Quantity: 1
- Layer 6: Block index 1 (Blue Rectangular - Horizontal) - Quantity: 1
- Layer 7: Block index 3 (Green Rectangular - Horizontal) - Quantity: 1

**List of Block Indices Required (in assembly order):** 10, 10, 6, 14, 14, 10, 14, 3, 10, 6, 3, 15, 1, 3
